summary: A very colorful and vibrant ENB preset.
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://i1056.photobucket.com/albums/t365/tristanfrancis/courierscolorenbpreset2-01-01.png[/img]

This is a preset for version 113 of the ENB Series. Please download the appropriate d3d9.DLL from the ENB series website.

Went for a more colorful and fantasy-ish style than my last preset, which you can find here:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/17953

If you have any questions, feel free to ask in the Comments section.
